# APIDriftSignal - Latency Drift and Health Monitor

APIDriftSignal highlights trends, spikes, and outages across multiple API endpoints and distributed services.

## Features
- Drift detection logic  
- JSON / CSV output  
- Real-time endpoint polling  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/34_APIDriftSignal.git
cd 34_APIDriftSignal
python monitor.py
